headline: Toro Q4 Earnings Miss Estimates, Professional Segment Sales Rise Y/Y
summary: TTC's Q4 results show a year-over-year increase in net sales. It also projects fiscal 2025 net sales growth of 0-1% and adjusted EPS between $4.25 and $4.40.
